---
// CTA.astro
---

<section class="py-section-gap-lg bg-background-main">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-gutter">
    <div class="bg-primary-container rounded-[40px] p-12 md:p-24 text-center relative overflow-hidden group shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20">
      <!-- Brand background lines -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden opacity-20">
        <svg class="absolute w-full h-full" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1000 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M-100 350C400 300 1000 100 1500 50" stroke="#e95c40" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="4"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 space-y-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight font-display">Prêt à propulser votre gestion paie ?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-sans">
          Rejoignez plus de 500 entreprises qui utilisent déjà la suite Fiabilis.ai pour sécuriser leur conformité sociale.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-6 pt-6">
          <a class="bg-brand-orange text-white px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-brand-orange/30 hover:-translate-y-1 font-sans" href="#">Prendre rendez-vous avec un expert</a>
          <a class="bg-white text-primary px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 font-sans" href="#">Télécharger notre brochure</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
